<p>We haven't seen you open a <%= @site_name %> email in a while, so we want to check in.</p>

<p>If you'd like to keep hearing from us, just let us know:</p>

<p><%= link_to "Keep me subscribed", @keep_url %></p>

<p>If we don't hear from you, we'll stop emailing you to keep our list healthy — no hard feelings. You can also <%= link_to "unsubscribe now", @unsubscribe_url %>.</p>
